{# What we offer #}
<section class="section section--alt" id="what-we-offer">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 data-animate="fade-up">What we offer professional instructors</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list" data-stagger>
      <li><strong>Strong brand presence.</strong> Each driving school in our group has built a real local reputation. You teach under a name people already trust.</li>
      <li><strong>Booking demand.</strong> Our group brands generate consistent bookings, so you spend less time chasing work and more time teaching.</li>
      <li><strong>Admin support.</strong> Our admin team handles bookings, payments, and follow-up. You stay focused on lessons.</li>
      <li><strong>Flexible work.</strong> Our schedules are built around the realities of professional instruction, not a head-office calendar.</li>
      <li><strong>Systems and scheduling.</strong> Shared booking and scheduling tools, set up to make your week easier.</li>
      <li><strong>Professional support.</strong> Real people on the other end of the phone when something needs sorting.</li>
      <li><strong>Multiple brands and locations.</strong> The group works across a number of brands and regions, with room to grow.</li>
      <li><strong>Opportunities beyond standard learner lessons over time.</strong> As we grow, instructors in our group can take on work beyond standard learner instruction.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

